# Team Draw NodeJs API with Typescript

This is the repository for the Team Draw NodeJs API with Typescript. This project is built using Node version 14.0.0 and npm version 6.0.0 or higher.

## Scripts

- `clean`: Removes the `dist` folder
- `build`: Runs `clean` and then compiles the TypeScript code into JavaScript code in the `dist` folder
- `dev`: Runs TypeScript in watch mode, so any changes made to the TypeScript code will be automatically compiled into JavaScript code
- `test`: Runs all tests in the project with Jest
- `test:unit`: Runs only unit tests with Jest
- `test:review`: Runs all tests in review mode with Jest
- `test:unit:review`: Runs only unit tests in review mode with Jest
- `lint`: Lints all TypeScript code in the project
- `lint:fix`: Automatically fixes any linting errors found in the TypeScript code
- `prettier`: Checks for formatting errors in all TypeScript files
- `prettier:fix` : Automatically fixes any formatting errors found in all TypeScript files
- `prepare` : Installs Husky to enable pre-commit hooks for linting and formatting checks

## Dependencies & DevDependencies

